| `app/globals.css` | CSS variables + utilitários |
| `components/Navbar` | Hide-on-scroll + mobile menu animado |
| `components/Hero` | Full-screen + texto staggered |
| `components/About` | Counters animados + imagem |
| `components/Services` | Grid de cards com stagger |
| `components/WhyUs` | Layout bicolor invertido |
| `components/Timeline` | Milestones alternados com linha central |
| `components/Team` | Hover revela bio |
| `components/Testimonials` | Carousel auto-play com dots |
| `components/Contact` | Formulário completo + mapa |
| `components/Footer` | Links + redes sociais |
| `components/WhatsAppFab` | Botão flutuante animado |